DIRECTORIES:
inout_util -> utilities for input and output operations, including a (very basic) customized reimplementation of some stdio.h functions
list -> implementation of 'List' data structure for generic types
struct_util -> utilities to manipulate custom data structures

FILES:
chat.h -> collection of all header files in this folder
macros.h -> all the macros used in the application
parameters.h -> constants and parameters used in the app. Some of them can be customized (recompile all if you change)
types.h -> custom data types defined in the app
